,"includ","red","rash","discol","bru","blist","us","first","tim","most","peopl","report","mild","goe","away","few","minut","hour","apply","patch","if","not","sery","burn","remov","cal","doct"]}},{"title":"Heart problems","black_box":false,"description":"Although Lidocaine used on the skin has less absorption in the body than if it was taken by mouth, there is still a certain amount that gets into the body. In people who have heart problems, especially irregular heartbeat, Lidocaine can work in a similar way as some medication used to treat the condition. Because of this, Lidocaine can increase your risk of irregular heartbeat especially if you are taking other medication to treat your heart condition. Tell your doctor about your heart condition before you start taking Lidocaine.","risk_factors":["History of heart problems","Using Lidocaine with drugs to treat irregular heartbeat"],"description_processed":{"orig":"Although Lidocaine used on the skin has less absorption in the body than if it was taken by mouth, there is still a certain amount that gets into the body. In people who have heart problems, especially irregular heartbeat, Lidocaine can work in a similar way as some medication used to treat the condition. Because of this, Lidocaine can increase your risk of irregular heartbeat especially if you are taking other medication to treat your heart condition. Tell your doctor about your heart condition before you start taking Lidocaine.","tokenized_and_stemmed":["although","lidocain","us","skin","less","absorb","body","tak","mou","certain","amount","get","in","peopl","heart","problem","espec","irregul","heartb","work","simil","med","tre","condit","becaus","increas","risk","tel","doct","start"]}}],"status":"Rx","images":null,"drug_class":["Pain"],"side_effects":[{"title":"Common side effects","points":[{"notes":"","placebo_n":null,"pt":"blister","placebo_value":null,"name":"Blisters","n":null,"hlt":"skin injuries nec","value":null,"dosage":"","source":"http://www.i